benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: PUT /1.0/kb/invoiceItems/{invoiceItemId}/customFields - Modify custom fields to invoice item

covered: Valid Request: Extensive test coverage for successful updates (TC01-TC05, TC21).
Non-Existing Resource: 404 scenarios covered (TC07, TC24, TC25).
Error Handling and Validation: 400/413/422-style errors covered (TC06, TC08, TC09, TC10, TC11, TC12, TC14).
Idempotency/Regression: Idempotent repeated PUTs (TC17) and regression case (TC18).
Performance: Large payload and parallel updates tested (TC20, TC21).
gaps: Partial Update: No explicit partial-update scenario is tested (only full-replace updates).
Explicit Concurrency Issues: No dedicated race-condition tests for concurrent updates on the same item.
Rate Limiting: No tests for rate limiting or throttling.
Caching Behavior: PUT caching headers (if applicable) not tested.
Authorization nuance: 403 Forbidden scenarios not specifically tested beyond 401.
recommendations: Add a dedicated Partial Update test or confirm the API does not support partial updates.
Add race-condition/concurrency tests (e.g., two clients updating the same item simultaneously).
Add rate-limiting/throttling tests for the endpoint.
Validate caching-related headers for PUT if applicable (ETag/Cache-Control).
Include tests for 403 Forbidden when user lacks permissions.
